  <h1>DevOps Lifecycle</h1>
  <p>This diagram visually explains each stage in the DevOps lifecycle.</p>
  <img src="file:///C:/Users/DELL/Downloads/Dailymotiv.drawio.png" alt="DevOps Lifecycle Diagram">

  <h2>Stages Explained</h2>
  <ul style="text-align: left; display: inline-block;">
    <li><strong>Plan:</strong> Define goals and gather requirements.</li>
    <li><strong>Develop:</strong> Write and manage code.</li>
    <li><strong>Build:</strong> Compile code and create build artifacts.</li>
    <li><strong>Test:</strong> Run automated/manual tests.</li>
    <li><strong>Release:</strong> Prepare for deployment.</li>
    <li><strong>Deploy:</strong> Move application to production.</li>
    <li><strong>Operate:</strong> Monitor application performance.</li>
    <li><strong>Monitor:</strong> Collect feedback for improvement.</li>
  </ul>
